FBIS4-60179 "drnes099_j_94006" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Russia Reportedly Recognizes South NC2105100094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 0940 GMT 21 May 94 NC2105100094 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Excerpt] Sanaa, 21 May (MENA)--Yemeni Planning Minister Dr. 'Abd-al-Karim al-Iryani said in Sanaa today that the Russian Federation Republic has recognized the Yemeni Democratic Republic. [passage omitted]
